          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <span style="color: blue;">
          v0.3.2:添加缘结神召唤活动<br>
          由于召唤活动通常会伴随三次up，所以将三次up和概率up合并了<br>
